<div><h3>ARTS 254 - Designer as Entrepreneur </h3>  <p><hr>Advanced applied problems involving the role of artists and designers as entrepreneurs. Students focus on using art and design skills to develop and sell original product designs. Students will create products and develop a business plan, marketing strategy, and test their concepts with consumers.</p>

